messages.message: Hey team. I'm trying to fix some bugs on release-22.10.0 but my python services can't run and fail with `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'foundation.document'` error. Probably related to https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C06FA6A23/p1665791701788239
